%p You can find your Speaker Rate id by looking at the text in the link on the right.
= image_tag "speaker_rate_find_id.png"
%p Just go to Speaker Rate, find your id, and enter it here. We can then sync your Speaker Rate profile with your account.

= form_for [@profile, @speaker_rate_profile] do |f|
  .label= f.label :speaker_rate_id, "Speaker Rate Id"
  .control= f.text_field :speaker_rate_id
  .submit= f.submit "Save", :disable_with => "Saving"
